    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>测试版包含内容：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.可解锁1、2、3号地块</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.可解锁最多6名村民</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3.最多拥有1个农田</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4.最多拥有1个熔炉和1个磨坊</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5.可探索5层矿洞</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6.可完成至少50个任务</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7.包含完整的制作、加工功能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>完整游戏介绍：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·收集资源</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269900/extras/2879a55a12a985a860367a40aee30e70.avif?t=1731985951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269900/extras_big/2879a55a12a985a860367a40aee30e70.avif?t=1731985951 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家需要努力收集各种资源，如树木、矿石等。深入黑暗且充满危险的矿洞，探索村庄和岛屿的各个角落，获取宝贵的资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·种植作物</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269900/extras/4cf51b5b76ce724b4b12a5a2d777c373.avif?t=1731985951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269900/extras_big/4cf51b5b76ce724b4b12a5a2d777c373.avif?t=1731985951 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在商人处购买心仪的作物种子，精心种植并照料它们。等待作物成熟后进行收割和加工，提升村庄的生产力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·制造与加工</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269900/extras/4fa414fbbb85525655da417615f0afac.avif?t=1731985951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269900/extras_big/4fa414fbbb85525655da417615f0afac.avif?t=1731985951 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用收集到的资源，制作村民所需的装备、食物和药品。村庄中还有许多加工建筑，通过解锁地块来使用这些设施，进一步提升生产效率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·建造与升级</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269900/extras/654bf53637067196548ec04ad1e0b67d.avif?t=1731985951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269900/extras_big/654bf53637067196548ec04ad1e0b67d.avif?t=1731985951 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个村民都有一个温馨的小家。玩家可以通过升级建筑和购买家具，打造更舒适的生活环境，提升村民的幸福感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>·战斗</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269900/extras/f02ba0f6e73e7db468eacad33291be8e.avif?t=1731985951\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269900/extras_big/f02ba0f6e73e7db468eacad33291be8e.avif?t=1731985951 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哥布林和骷髅在各地盘踞。通过战斗击败这些敌人，不仅可以获得丰富的战利品，还能夺回被它们占领的宝箱和土地，扩展村庄的领土。</p>",
